HEADWORD: 20
<hw>20</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>one more than nineteen;
denoting a quantity consisting of twenty items or units; -- representing
the number twenty as Arabic numerals</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> twenty, xx, score</syn>⟦br⟧
